These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, mechanic, lawyer, analyst
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, swisher, prince
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, basketball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the entrepreneur is the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job    | mechanic  | analyst | lawyer    | entrepreneur       |
| Cigar         | baccarat | prince    | swisher      | oliveros |
| Sport   | water-polo   | basketball | biathlon | lacrosse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, baking, hiking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, september, august
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, horse, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Hobby        | baking   | rock-climbing | fishing     | hiking      |
| Birthday         | november | september | august | january |
| Pet   | ferret    | guinea-pig   | horse     | chinchilla      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, red, white, brown
City: boston, san-francisco, berlin, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, sprite, juice
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes brown is the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | fuchsia | red | white | brown |
| City   | new-york       | san-francisco    | boston | berlin     |
| Beverage   | water | sprite    | juice | milk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
House: cottage, wooden, colonial, futuristic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero, crime, horror
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine, black, pink
1. the colonial house is the person who likes pink##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the wooden house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is the colonial house##1
7. the colonial house is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| House         | cottage | futuristic | colonial | wooden |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero     | horror      | fantasy     | crime      |
| Color   | aquamarine | ebony         | pink      | black        |

