.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
House: wooden, art-deco, cape-cod, modern
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, accountant, pilot, electrician
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, canasta, backgammon
1. the accountant is on the far right##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the chef##1
4. the person playing bridge is the pilot##1
5. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the wooden house is the accountant##1
7. the modern house is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| House         | cape-cod   | modern | art-deco  | wooden      |
| Job   | pilot  | chef        | electrician  | accountant       |
| Game         | bridge | canasta    | domino | backgammon |

