.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, chinese, japanese, american
4 different games are played: chess, go, backgammon, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, cooking, writing, photography
1. the polish is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the american##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the chinese is on the far left##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the japanese##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person playing go##1
8. the american is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality           | chinese | japanese | american | polish |
| Game   | snooker   | backgammon  | go | chess   |
| Hobby   | photography   | rock-climbing     | writing | cooking       |

