.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, baccarat, pall-mall, game
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, canadian, nigerian
City: hannover, venice, edinburgh, new-york
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to venice is the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the egyptian is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the indian is on the right of the egyptian##1
8. the egyptian is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar          | alhambra  | game | pall-mall   | baccarat     |
| Nationality         | nigerian | egyptian   | indian  | canadian |
| City   | edinburgh         | hannover  | venice | new-york  |

