.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, february, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, biathlon, sailing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, reggae, funk
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the fan of funk is the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of funk##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | may | february     | january | december |
| Sport   | sailing  | skateboarding | biathlon       | rowing    |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | funk | country    | reggae |

