.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, software-developer, musician, bartender
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, pony, fish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, water, lemonade
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the bartender##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person drinking water is the software-developer##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the musician##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job          | musician        | bartender   | software-developer  | mechanic   |
| Pet   | snake         | fish     | rabbit    | pony       |
| Beverage         | milk | 7up | water | lemonade |

