.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea, daffodil, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, june, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, ice-hockey, parkour
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | azalea    | daffodil | bellflower | daisy        |
| Birthday       | july | may  | february | june     |
| Sport        | rugby    | ice-hockey   | parkour  | rowing |

