.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, ambient, gospel, salsa
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, fanta, iced-tea
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, craftsman, cottage
1. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the craftsman house##1
8. the person drinking fanta is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | blues  | salsa | ambient  | gospel |
| Beverage       | fanta | cola        | iced-tea | mirinda       |
| House   | cape-cod   | ranch-style          | cottage          | craftsman       |

