.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, rat, chinchilla, frog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, chaman, davidoff, cain
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, banana, orange, lemon
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the pony is the person eating orange##1
7. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog   | chinchilla   | pony | rat |
| Cigar   | davidoff | swisher | chaman   | cain |
| Food   | lemon     | nectarine  | orange  | banana  |

