.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, go, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, indian, pakistani, argentine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, march, april
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the argentine##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the indian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the polish##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Game         | bridge | backgammon    | scrabble        | go |
| Nationality   | indian     | pakistani     | argentine        | polish   |
| Birthday         | january   | february | march | april  |

