.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, sprite, milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, zinnia, orchid
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, banana, corn, kiwi
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating banana##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | milk  | iced-tea    | sprite    |
| Flower   | orchid | zinnia  | sunflower  | balloon-flower |
| Food     | kiwi  | banana | corn | pineapple        |

