.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officercher, project-manager, police-officer, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, punk, electronic
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, photography, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the police-officer##1
2. the police-officer is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the fan of electronic is the paramedic##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
7. the police-officercher is the fan of ambient##1
8. the fan of punk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job      | police-officercher        | paramedic    | project-manager | police-officer      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | electronic   | r&b  | punk  |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | hiking | photography   | chess |

