.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, card-games, chess
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, tram, train
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, turtle, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Hobby           | writing  | card-games  | filmmaking | chess |
| Transport   | train   | ship | snowmobile   | tram      |
| Pet         | bird | turtle    | fish   | guinea-pig         |

 